title: Jeremy Spencer
description:
Very Old LP of Jeremy Spencer, who was a member of Fleetwood Mac from 1967-71
Released in 1970, this was his first solo album and the first solo album by a current member of Fleetwood Mac

Unfortunately full with Clicks, Hiss and even jumps over a track here and there.


Jeremy Spencer - vocals, Slide Guitar, Piano 
Mick Fleetwood - drums, Congas, percussion 
John McVie - Bass guitar 
Danny Kirwan - Guitar, Backing vocals 
Peter Green - Banjo on track 4 
Stephen Gregory - Saxophone 

Produced by Jeremy Spencer

Label: Reprise Records
